'''陰莖折斷'''指的是覆蓋[[陰莖海綿體|陰莖海綿體]]的白膜其中之一或兩者全部破裂的情況。病因是[[陰莖|陰莖]]勃起後遭到劇烈的打擊<ref name="Greenberg's Text-Atlas of Emergency Medicine">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tjZttRRH8H8C&pg=PA318&hl=en|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|date=2005|isbn=978-0-7817-4586-4|language=en|first=Michael I.|last=Greenberg|title=Greenberg's Text-atlas of Emergency Medicine|pages=318|access-date=2020-06-27|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730214940/https://books.google.com/books?id=tjZttRRH8H8C&pg=PA318&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有時也會伴隨著[[尿道|尿道]]阻斷或陰莖背部神經、靜動脈血管受損。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Penile fracture and testicular rupture|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10367369/|last=Haas|first=C. A.|last2=Brown|first2=S. L.|date=1999-04|journal=World Journal of Urology|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s003450050114|volume=17|pages=101–106|issn=0724-4983|pmid=10367369|last3=Spirnak|first3=J. P.|access-date=2020-06-27|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627035427/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10367369/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

陰道性交、[[肛交|肛交]]和粗暴的[[自慰|手淫]]是最常見的原因。<ref name="Greenberg's Text-Atlas of Emergency Medicine"/> 陰莖折斷後陰莖會迅速疲軟，并伴隨著劇烈疼痛，常常也會出現不同類型的[[血腫|血腫]]。<ref name="Greenberg's Text-Atlas of Emergency Medicine"/>

==治療==

陰莖折斷屬於{{le|醫療應急|Medical emergency}}事故，需要立即進行手術對受損的陰莖進行修復。不進行手術治療可能有10–50%的機率導致[[勃起功能障礙|勃起功能障礙]]、永久性[[陰莖彎曲|陰莖彎曲]]、尿道受損和性交疼痛。得到有效治療的患者的併發症率為11%。<ref name="Greenberg's Text-Atlas of Emergency Medicine"/><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JnTMQOMcYZwC&pg=PA305&hl=en|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|date=2008|isbn=978-0-7817-6275-5|language=en|first=Andrew B.|last=Peitzman|first2=Michael|last2=Rhodes|first3=C. William|last3=Schwab|title=The Trauma Manual: Trauma and Acute Care Surgery|pages=305|access-date=2020-06-27|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223080530/https://books.google.com/books?id=JnTMQOMcYZwC&pg=PA305&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

